claim.claim-text:
11. A method of measuring and correcting a voltage from a power supply to a circuit configured to manage a battery pack, the method comprising:
measuring, by a processor, the voltage of the power supply;
determining, by the processor, a state of the circuit;
determining, by the processor, a correction value based on the state of the circuit; and
correcting, by the processor, the measured voltage based on the correction value.
